.SH NAME
tag add \- Add tags to a book
.SH SYNOPSIS
alexandria> tag add
.SH DESCRIPTION
.TP
Prompts for a book reference (ID, ISBN, title, or author) and comma-separated tags.
.TP
Adds only tags that are not already present.
